                  |                          
                  li(type='square')
                    | Oversee layout (artwork, design, photography) and check content for accuracy and errors
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Proofread, edit and improve stories or pieces
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Recruit and manage writers and reporters
                  |                          
                  li(type='square')
