                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Comply with media law and ethical guidelines
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Meet deadlines
                |                     
                br
                |                     
                b Requirements:
                |                     
                ul
                  li(type='square') Some working experience as an editor
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Strong writing/editing/proofreading skills and an excellent portfolio
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Proven familiarity with SEO and social media best practices
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Excellent written skills in English
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') An eye for detail along with critical thinking
                  |                          
                  li(type='square') Prioritizing and multitasking
