                  |                   
                  li(type='square') Create site layout/user interface by using standard HTML/CSS practices
                  |                   
                  li(type='square') Integrate data from various back-end services and databases
                  |                   
                  li(type='square') Gather and refine specifications and requirements based on technical needs
                  |                   
                  li(type='square') Create and maintain software documentation
                  |                   
                  li(type='square') Be responsible for maintaining, expanding, and scaling our site
